16
00:01:02,837 --> 00:01:04,591
Constanza Fuentes?
Constanza Fuentes?

17
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:07,394
As in Party Chairwoman Fuentes?
做党主席的那位Fuentes?

18
00:01:09,599 --> 00:01:10,911
Well? What did she want?
Well?她有什么事?

19
00:01:11,793 --> 00:01:16,176
