她问我是否曾考虑过竞选公职.

20
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:19,366
Any particular one?
具体什么职位?

21
00:01:19,824 --> 00:01:22,679
Attorney General of the State of Massachusetts.
Massachusetts州首席检察官.

22
00:01:22,853 --> 00:01:24,422
